---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Features - Lexara" 
  description="Discover the powerful features that make Engage the leading AI-powered legal client intake platform. Smart conversations, conflict detection, and seamless integrations."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-lexara-light to-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-lexara-secondary mb-6">
        Powerful Features for Modern Law Firms
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-lexara-gray mb-8">
        Engage combines advanced AI with legal expertise to deliver the most 
        comprehensive client intake solution for law firms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Features -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <!-- AI-Powered Conversations -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lexara-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lexara-secondary mb-6">
            Intelligent Conversations
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-lexara-gray mb-6">
            Our AI assistant conducts natural, empathetic conversations that feel human while 
            systematically gathering critical case information. Trained specifically for legal intake, 
            it adapts to your firm's practice areas and communication style.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Natural language processing optimized for legal intake</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Multi-phase security for sensitive information</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Resumable conversations with persistent tokens</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-4 rounded-lg rounded-br-none max-w-sm">
              I understand you're dealing with a workplace injury. Can you tell me when this occurred and what type of work you were doing?
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg rounded-bl-none max-w-sm ml-auto">
              It happened last Tuesday while I was operating heavy machinery at the construction site.
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-4 rounded-lg rounded-br-none max-w-sm">
              Thank you for that information. Were there any witnesses present, and have you received medical attention for your injuries?
            </div>
            <div class="text-center py-2">
              <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                ðŸ”’ Conversation secured after authentication
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Conflict Detection -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lexara-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lexara-secondary mb-6">
            Automatic Conflict Detection
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-lexara-gray mb-6">
            Protect your firm with real-time conflict checking using advanced vector search technology. 
            Our system identifies potential conflicts across clients, opposing parties, and related entities 
            before they become ethical problems.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Real-time vector database search</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Fuzzy matching for name variations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Configurable conflict escalation rules</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-1 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary">Conflict Check Results</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="font-medium text-green-800">John Smith</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs">Clear</span>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="font-medium text-yellow-800">ABC Corporation</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs">Review</span>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="font-medium text-red-800">Former Client Match</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs">Conflict</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Practice Area Customization -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lexara-secondary mb-6">
            Practice Area Intelligence
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-lexara-gray mb-6">
            Engage adapts to your firm's specific practice areas with customizable conversation flows, 
            specialized questioning patterns, and targeted information gathering for different legal matters.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Personal injury, family law, business law templates</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Customizable knowledge base and supporting documents</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lexara-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lexara-gray">Dynamic goal adaptation based on case type</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-6">Practice Areas</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg text-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lexara-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-lexara-secondary">Personal Injury</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg text-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lexara-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-lexara-secondary">Family Law</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg text-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-lexara-secondary">Business Law</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg text-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-lexara-secondary">Estate Planning</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-lexara-gray mt-4 text-center">
            + Custom practice areas and specialties
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Features Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lexara-secondary mb-4">
          Everything You Need for Client Intake
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-lexara-gray">
          Comprehensive features designed specifically for legal professionals
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lexara-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 00-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">Analytics & Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Track conversation metrics, conversion rates, and client acquisition insights with detailed analytics.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lexara-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">White-Label Branding</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Customize the interface with your firm's branding, colors, and messaging for a seamless client experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">API & Integrations</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Seamlessly integrate with your existing practice management software, CRM, and other legal tech tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">Mobile Responsive</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Perfect experience across all devices - desktop, tablet, and mobile for clients on-the-go.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">Enterprise Security</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Bank-level encryption, HIPAA compliance, and secure authentication protect your client data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192L5.636 18.364M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lexara-secondary mb-3">24/7 Support</h3>
          <p class="text-lexara-gray">
            Expert support team available around the clock to help with setup, training, and ongoing assistance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-lexara-primary">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Experience the Power of AI-Driven Client Intake
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
        See how Engage can transform your law firm's client acquisition and intake process.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/signup" class="bg-white text-lexara-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
          Start Free Trial
        </a>
        <a href="/demo" class="border border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-lexara-primary transition-colors">
          Watch Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>